School Improvement Network, founded in 1991, is a privately owned national education company based in Midvale, Utah, USA. The company develops, distributes and markets various professional development product lines. Historically, School Improvement Network produced professional development training videos, but since 2007 has pioneered services in online educational administrator and teacher training video content.[1] School Improvement Network is a privately held company and as such does not publicly disclose its financial statements.
